{
  "body" : "为【{{topic}}】生成一张高质量中文健身训练信息图。\n\nThe graphic should be both professional and practical for a normal adult to use as a training reference. Unless otherwise specified, assume the audience is【{{audience_level}}】, the goal is【{{training_goal}}】, the level is beginner to intermediate, the setting is a normal gym, and the total session length should stay within {{session_minutes}} minutes.\n\nChoose the output format automatically based on the training topic:\n\n1. If the topic is a muscle group or body part, such as chest, lats, biceps, abs, shoulders, or legs, generate a training-plan infographic for that body part.\n2. If the topic is an exercise or skill goal, such as pull-up, push-up, dips, or squat, generate an exercise-unlock or progression-plan infographic.\n\nUse a clear, modern, professional, easy-to-read Chinese infographic style in vertical format. The visual design should be clean and suitable for social sharing or personal training reference. Do not write long paragraphs. Each module should use short concise phrases, and numerical information should be prominent.\n\nThe infographic must include:\nA. 标题区：主标题（{{topic}}）+ 副标题（一句话训练定位）\nB. 训练目标区：{{training_goal}}，配 1–2 个量化指标\nC. 热身区：3–5 个针对性热身动作（每个 1 行说明 + 组数）\nD. 主训练区：4 到 6 个核心动作（每个动作必须有：动作名 + 组数×次数 + 关键提示，配一个简笔示意小图）\nE. 进阶 / 解锁逻辑区：本周到下周怎么加重 / 加次数（量化的进阶路径）\nF. 替代动作区：每个核心动作配 1 个家庭 / 无器械替代版\nG. 执行提醒区：3–5 条执行要点（呼吸、节奏、关节位置、常见错误）\nH. 恢复建议区：补水 / 拉伸 / 间隔时间 / 睡眠建议\nI. 视觉设计：整体风格采用【{{design_style}}】；现代、干净、专业、卡片式模块布局\n\n色彩与排版规范\n- 标题大字用稳重黑体，正文用现代无衬线，数字（组数次数）必须显眼。\n- 模块之间用细线 / 留白分隔，不用厚边框、不用塑料色块。\n- icon 风格统一（线稿就全线稿，扁平就全扁平，不混搭）。\n- 中文必须可读、无乱码、无错别字、无拼音夹杂。\n\n严格规避\n- 不要做成 PPT 模板感、不要免费教程感、不要表情包堆砌。\n- 不要把动作示意画成完美健美明星照片（用线稿小图即可）。\n- 不要解剖图夸张（吓人不专业）。\n- 不要塞满促销 / 课程报名信息（这是训练参考，不是广告）。\n- 不要文字压住示意图。\n\nThe final result should be a complete infographic rather than plain text paragraphs. 输出：2:3 竖版。\n\n——————\n训练主题：{{topic}}\n受众：{{audience_level}}\n目标：{{training_goal}}\n时长：{{session_minutes}} 分钟\n风格：{{design_style}}\n",
